HEADWORD: Wheelbarrow
<hw>Wheel"bar`row</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A light vehicle
for conveying small loads. It has two handles and one wheel, and is
rolled by a single person.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wheel base</ent>⟦br⟧
